    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >INTRODUCTION</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >此为庆祝《血腥画家》角色创建10周年与回馈粉丝们的支持而制作的粉丝向官方恐怖恋爱视觉小说游戏，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >是根据2017年版本的故事做的番外篇衍生。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214880/extras/750d88482384e5465a79223f2fca75ad.poster.avif?t=1760246490\" width=616 height=274 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214880/extras/750d88482384e5465a79223f2fca75ad.webm?t=1760246490\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3214880/extras/750d88482384e5465a79223f2fca75ad.mp4?t=1760246490\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >STORY</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你不幸的被杀人魔囚禁了起来，你必须在7天内提高存活率。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的选择会决定他对你的处置与你们最终的关系，你与他最终的关系会是……？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >杀人魔与猎物之间的关系是否会产生变化呢？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >CONTENT WARNINGS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >．本游戏含部分血腥画面描述。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >．遇到杀人魔请先报警，想与杀人魔发展出浪漫关系是不切实际的。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >．这是一款恋爱游戏♥</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >．全英文语音。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >．总共有14张精美CG图。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >ESTIMATED PLAY TIME</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >完成一个好结局大约40分钟。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >NUMBER OF ENDINGS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >6个坏结局 + 4个好结局。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >STREAMING PERMISSION</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >欢迎直播游玩本游戏！同时若有遇到BUG请留言回报通知我们。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >选择英文语言的玩家建议至设定将文本速度调整至最快。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >OPERATING SYSTEMS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Windows 7及以上。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >CREDITS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>研发、故事、程式：</strong>迪鹿DeluCat @DeluCatOfficial</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>美术：</strong>牛奶 @milk890522</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>背景：</strong>kurumi2179、迪鹿DeluCat</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>标准字：</strong>サヤカ @laipeng16</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>配音：</strong>Easton @eastonandemmary</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>预告片：</strong>ZAO @ZAO_Studio_</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>字型：</strong>翰字铸造 - 台北正黑体</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>特别感谢：</strong>南翁、LoS-Light</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>游戏测试：</strong>七七</p>",
